data.description: Buyers financing fell through.Nice 3 bedroom 2 full bath comfortable home in Idleloch subdivision. Master bath has a walk in shower. Storm windows to help reduce heating and cooling costs.Garage door opener.Very quiet neighborhood just minutes away from Atascocita and close to Lake Houston. Good schools, nice family friendly neighborhood.
